		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />phpBB 2 was aware of your current session and your previous session. Any post older than the start of your previous session was deemed read. New phpBB is more accurate about this.<br /><br />What does &quot;Mark forums read&quot; on the main page do?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
