	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, I like the new behavior better. In the old forum, sometimes I didn't have time to read all new messages in the same session and because of that I would miss some of them, since they weren't marked as new anymore the next time I opened the forum.<br /><br />Now, I can read all the messages of my interest, taking as much time as needed, and once I know that only the topics I don't care about have new messages I click the &quot;Mark forums read&quot; option to clear everything.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


