	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think he may be referring to the fact that under &quot;View unread posts&quot;, if you click on the <strong>post subject/thread name itself</strong> it does not mark the thread as read -- instead, you have to click on the last page number shown under the post subject/thread name to get that to happen.  (Or in the case there's been multiple pages of posts since your last visit, you have to visit all of them, if I remember right)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


